  "summary": {
    "en": "Samphanthawong is one of the 50 districts (khet) of Bangkok, Thailand. Regarded as Bangkok's Chinatown, it is the smallest district by area in Thailand. Neighbouring districts are Pom Prap Sattru Phai, Bang Rak, Khlong San, and Phra Nakhon.",
